    <title>网易云音乐MP3音频获取</title>
    <url>/2023/08/05/%E7%BD%91%E6%98%93%E4%BA%91%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90MP3%E9%9F%B3%E9%A2%91%E8%8E%B7%E5%8F%96/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>网易云音乐是有个网页版的，地址是：<a href="https://music.163.com/">https://music.163.com/</a>。电脑如果装了IDM下载器，能听的可以直接用IDM捕获MP3。那如果没有IDM就没法获取了吗？</p>
<p>不存在的，今天我就来教大家实现，无IDM获取网易云音乐MP3音频文件。</p>
<span id="more"></span>
<h2 id="%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86" tabindex="-1">原理<a class="header-anchor" href="#%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86" aria-hidden="true"></a></h2>
<h3 id="%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90id" tabindex="-1">音乐ID<a class="header-anchor" href="#%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90id" aria-hidden="true"></a></h3>
<p>电脑进入网页版网易云音乐，随便进一首歌，就会发现地址栏出现类似如下链接：</p>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="https://music.163.com/#/song?id=1950897620">https://music.163.com/#/song?id=1950897620</a></p>
</blockquote>
<p>链接中<code>?id=</code>后面的数字是不固定的，这首歌是<code>1950897620</code>，每首歌都是不一样的。<br>
此处，大家一定猜到这串数字是音乐的ID</p>
<p>为什么我要给大家讲这个ID呢？那肯定是后面要用嘛……</p>
<h3 id="%E7%9B%B4%E9%93%BE" tabindex="-1">直链<a class="header-anchor" href="#%E7%9B%B4%E9%93%BE" aria-hidden="true"></a></h3>
<p>随便在百度上搜一下就可以找到。<br>
链接格式如下：</p>
<p><code>https://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=音乐ID.mp3</code></p>
<p>以上面的那首歌为例，它的音乐ID是<code>1950897620</code>，则它的直链就是<a href="https://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1950897620.mp3">https://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1950897620.mp3</a></p>
<p>不信的可以自己试一下，右键将链接另存为即可。</p>
<p>可惜，这个方法仅限于能直接听不用会员的音乐，会员音乐会404……</p>
<h2 id="%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8" tabindex="-1">应用<a class="header-anchor" href="#%E5%BA%94%E7%94%A8" aria-hidden="true"></a></h2>
<h3 id="python%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F" tabindex="-1">Python程序<a class="header-anchor" href="#python%E7%A8%8B%E5%BA%8F" aria-hidden="true"></a></h3>
<p>讲完了获取直链的方法，相信大部分读者都已经学会了。<br>
但这就是极限了吗？</p>
<p>学过Python的基本上都知道怎么下载文件：<br>
示例如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line">url = <span class="string">&#x27;https://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=1950897620.mp3&#x27;</span></span><br><span class="line">r = requests.get(url, allow_redirect=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;/path/to/file.mp3&#x27;</span>, <span class="string">&#x27;wb&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line">    f.write(r)</span><br><span class="line">    f.close()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>这里不详细说每行代码的作用了。</p>
<p>利用上述代码，我们就可以稍作改进完成如下代码：</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests     <span class="comment"># 导入requests库</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">id</span> = <span class="built_in">input</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;请输入音乐ID：&#x27;</span>)     <span class="comment"># 询问音乐id，并保存到变量</span></span><br><span class="line">path = <span class="built_in">input</span>(<span class="string">&#x27;请输入保存路径：&#x27;</span>)     <span class="comment"># 询问保存路径，并保存到变量</span></span><br><span class="line">url = <span class="string">&#x27;https://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=&#x27;</span>+<span class="built_in">id</span>+<span class="string">&#x27;.mp3&#x27;</span>     <span class="comment"># 应用直链</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 获取链接内容并保存到文件</span></span><br><span class="line">r = requests.get(url, allow_redirect=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(path, <span class="string">&#x27;wb&#x27;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line">    f.write(r)</span><br><span class="line">    f.close()</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p>我们甚至可以引入<code>tkinter</code>等GUI库。</p>
<figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> tkinter</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> tkinter.simpledialog</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> tkinter.filedialog</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> webbrowser</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> win10toast</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> threading</span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> os</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">toaster = win10toast.ToastNotifier()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">dmp3 = []</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">download</span>(<span class="params"><span class="built_in">id</span>, isid</span>):</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="built_in">id</span> <span class="keyword">is</span> <span class="keyword">not</span> <span class="literal">None</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(tkinter.filedialog.asksaveasfilename(defaultextension=<span class="string">&quot;.mp3&quot;</span>, filetypes=[(<span class="string">&quot;音频文件&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;.mp3&quot;</span>)]),</span><br><span class="line">                  <span class="string">&quot;wb&quot;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line">            f.write(requests.get(<span class="string">&quot;http://music.163.com/song/media/outer/url?id=&quot;</span> + <span class="built_in">id</span>).content)</span><br><span class="line">            f.close()</span><br><span class="line">        toaster.show_toast(<span class="string">&quot;网易云音乐 MP3音频下载工具&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;下载完成！&quot;</span>, duration=<span class="number">10</span>, threaded=<span class="literal">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">afid</span>():</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="built_in">id</span> = tkinter.simpledialog.askstring(<span class="string">&quot;输入音乐ID（不支持会员歌曲）&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;音乐ID：&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span> <span class="built_in">id</span>:</span><br><span class="line">        dmp3.append(threading.Thread(name=<span class="string">&quot;Download MP3 (ID:&quot;</span> + <span class="built_in">id</span> + <span class="string">&quot;)&quot;</span>, target=download, args=(<span class="built_in">id</span>, <span class="built_in">id</span>), daemon=<span class="literal">True</span>))</span><br><span class="line">        dmp3[<span class="built_in">len</span>(dmp3) - <span class="number">1</span>].start()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">def</span> <span class="title function_">gotogw</span>():</span><br><span class="line">    webbrowser.<span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&quot;https://music.163.com/&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">tk = tkinter.Tk()</span><br><span class="line">tkinter.Button(tk, text=<span class="string">&quot;下载MP3文件&quot;</span>, command=afid).pack()</span><br><span class="line">tkinter.Button(tk, text=<span class="string">&quot;打开官方网站&quot;</span>, command=gotogw).pack()</span><br><span class="line">tk.title(<span class="string">&quot;网易云音乐MP3音频下载工具&quot;</span>)</span><br><span class="line">tk.attributes(<span class="string">&quot;-topmost&quot;</span>, <span class="number">1</span>)</span><br><span class="line">tk.resizable(<span class="literal">True</span>, <span class="literal">False</span>)</span><br><span class="line">tk.mainloop()</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/katex/dist/katex.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="//cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/markdown-it-texmath/css/texmath.min.css">
]]></content>
